Class Ant

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mycompany.a3.GameObject
      • com.mycompany.a3.Movable
        • com.mycompany.a3.Ant
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICollider, IDrawable, ISteerable

    public class Ant
extends Movable
implements ISteerable
    This class contains the Ant Object. It extends the Movable class since it is movable, along with implementing ISteerable to give the user the ability to steer the ant.
    Author:
    Alex Furmuzan
